Your new company
One of the Top Tier Chinese Retail and Corporate Banks, covering products ranging from retail lending, corporate loans, M&A, project financing and other capital market products;
Steadily expanding in Hong Kong and Asia as well as globally;

Your new role

Report directly to Department Head of Retail Credit, you will manage credit approval and credit policy team under retail credit risk function;
Responsible for managerial role, maintain the smooth process of retail credit business;
Ensure credit monitoring, early warming systems are in place;
Support on-going system enhancement for efficient approval process.


What you'll need to succeed

15+ years retail credit (approval, policy, portfolio management or collections) experience in reputable bank covering Retail Credit or Commercial Credit;
Solid people management experience;
Fluent in Chinese and English


What you'll get in return

Rare Vacancy
Competitive salary and high annual discretionary bonus
Managerial role


